docs.title: Welcome to Trustgen Documentation
docs.text: Welcome to the official documentation for Trustgen. This documentation site contains comprehensive guides and information about our projects and tools.

docs.title: Getting Started
docs.text: Choose a section from the navigation menu to begin exploring our documentation.

docs.title: Features
docs.text:
• Comprehensive documentation
  • Easy navigation
  • Dark/light theme support
  • Full-text search
  • Mobile friendly

docs.title: Contributing
docs.text: We welcome contributions to our documentation! Please visit our GitHub repository to get started.

docs.title: Support
docs.text: If you need help or have questions, please open an issue in our GitHub repository.
